data.title: 403 Gunning Bedford Dr, Dover, DE 19904
data.meta_description: 403 Gunning Bedford Dr, Dover, DE 19904 is pending. Zillow has 34 photos of this 4 beds, 3 baths, 1,832 Square Feet single family home with a list price of $319,900.
data.text: Welcome to this completely rehabbed tri-level gem, situated on the largest lot in Rodney Village. This immaculate, move-in ready home features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, designed with modern living in mind. The lower level offers a serene retreat with a spacious main bedroom complete with a full bath and a cozy family room, perfect for relaxation. The main floor is a stunning open area that will leave you in awe. Gather around the kitchen island and enjoy watching the chef in action in the brand-new kitchen, boasting granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an abundance of cabinetry to delight any cook. Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, including one with a walk-in closet, and a huge full bath. The home features LPV flooring throughout, except in the bedrooms, adding a touch of elegance and practicality. The new recessed lighting enhances the home's modern appeal. This one-of-a-kind home in Rodney Village is a must-see to truly appreciate its beauty and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your new home!
